{"tid":1353524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重申：不容暴力，煽動暴力的政客可恥！","createTime":"2019-07-23T03:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T05:26:57.000Z","uid":107060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bd0e736e5acf13adb7998e012cb75357591673d9","tid":1353524,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:34:14.000Z","msg":"方國珊<br />\n20小時 &middot; <br />\n【看圖作故事時間】<br />\n<br />\n從政十年，作為無黨派人士，一直抱著「對事不對人」的原則，只要民生議題有得傾，大原則一致，就可以企在同一陣線，一同為市民發聲。<br />\n<br />\n今日將軍澳群組專針對我的常客「張X董」（早前搞亂業委會個位），話我同疑似支持昨晚元朗暴力行為的立法會議員何君堯係一伙，真係得啖笑。<br />\n<br />\n年中出席唔少活動，我同曾俊華、長毛握過手、同胡官見過黎、天琦坐過我隔離。下面有幾張圖，大家作故事吧！<br />\n我先！<br />\n<br />\n「朋友傳給我，原來方國珊同熱血公民都係一伙」<br />\n<br />\n重申：不容暴力，煽動暴力的政客可恥！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rC15Bk2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrC15Bk2.png&h=7645379a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c388fba407ff913b37e44f52d12d11ddfe4d826","tid":1353524,"uid":32861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:36:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">721宣言</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUigsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=9d812b96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a><br />\n<br />\n條片只有<span style=\"color: green;\">3000views</span> <br />\n但留言勁多5毛 某程度證明有用<br />\n（排序較新至舊 你會發現多得過份）<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手留言 引啲5毛一齊推上<span style=\"color: maroon;\">Youtube熱門</span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">歡迎轉發及引用推Post</code></pre>"},{"pid":"a6be7a97b9b4abf723c1295caafb6238205ef405","tid":1353524,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf8b8cace8d048fdd0a076234dab726e0b440e2","tid":1353524,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0